{"tid":1631523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對家千方百計想瓦解運動, 但4個月快過去了....","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:25:31.000Z","uid":51963,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ac4962fa675279fe267cf8329bf7b1235a8b7e","tid":1631523,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"睇得出佢地好心急<br />\n而家對家就係想我地暴力, 刻意製造流血畫面, 店鋪/港鐵被縱火/破壞<br />\n又有5毛帶風向, 又有鬼滲透<br />\n但過去4個月全因我地團結, 大家都冇割, 絕對唔會今日因為小小野而割<br />\n今日有D野係唔完美，可接受，但亦都要改善<br />\n唔完美係太多暴力畫面比人影到大造文章, 可接受係因為我地大方向正確<br />\n要改善就係下次做得大方得體一D, 鋪頭搵幾間最仆街集中攪左先<br />\n(我建議伍淑清條老臭閪棋下D鋪, 因為佢聯合國鳩UP講大話抺黑手足)<br />\n口角不必動武, 最後記住開遮"},{"pid":"51814de17adef9a20c4bc1cdfde09a1ffdf5df00","tid":1631523,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"35a78af375d06afa9ba26e35a866050cbe9f5990","tid":1631523,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"220facab0fade0b80bf38286bffa9e005718f18c","tid":1631523,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:08.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"5a0eb8e731fded4e5798a74556a857205cdad1c8","tid":1631523,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a6769e1c26b2597a938b8c0825fa62dd553eef5b","tid":1631523,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"64e69e3e2d1869cc6780f059416fe12bb2fa92f0","tid":1631523,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea155d5b079f4090a4d5ed82b23c452ad60c75a8","tid":1631523,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">港豬們好耐未三罷啦</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n香港人．<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span><br />\n香港人．三罷</span>"}]}